    {
      "para_id": "Q002014.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Dagan , the lord of the great gods , her personal god , En-ana-tuma , the beloved en priestess of Nanna in Urim , child of Išme-Dagan , king of Sumer and Akkad , built the E-eš-medaĝala , her holy storehouse , and dedicated it to him for the well-being of Gungunum , the powerful man , king of Urim and for her ( own ) well-being ."
    }
  ],
